### Get user sales statistics
# Shows order count and total money spent per user
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get product sales statistics
# Shows order count and turnover per product
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

